			<div class="project_desc_p">
				<p>Pirex is a ranking information retrieval system for searching small collections of full-text documents. More specifically, the system allows the storing of books from the website www.gutenburg.org and allows the retrieval and ranking of specific passages based on search criteria specified by the user. Our group was responsible for creating the GUI as well as the backend, implementing structures such as an inverted index 
