				<p style="font-size: 16px;">Database Design and Application, Spring 2019</p>
			</div>
			<div class="project_desc_y">
				<p>Whats in Your Neck of the Woods is a three-tier application that uses a database management system. Our group chose to design an application that would allow users to look up and compare crime statistics of areas of interest within certain search criteria. Our group was responsible for retrieving relevant data, designing the SQL tables and queries as well as designing the web page.   
